cho_description:
A female head from around 200 BC, discovered at Benha-El-Assal.

Length: 23 centimetres Width: 17.5 centimetres Depth: 8.5 centimetres 

COL: [YCA60281](http://www.britishmuseum.org/research/collection_online/collection_object_details.aspx?partId=1&objectId=120280)

136 photographs taken by Daniel O'Flynn, Sony A6000. Model assembled by Daniel Pett using Photoscan pro.
